# AnimeKai CloudStream Extension

A CloudStream 3 plugin that brings [AnimeKai](https://animekai.be) into the CloudStream app.  
Stream free HD anime (Sub & Dub) — TV series, Movies, OVAs, ONAs, Specials.

---

## Features
- 🏠 **Home page** — Latest Updates, New Releases, Ongoing, TV, Movies, OVAs
- 🔍 **Search** — full-text search across AnimeKai's library
- 📺 **Episode list** — all episodes, automatically paginated
- ▶️ **Video links** — auto-detects embedded players (Vidstream, Filemoon, Streamtape, etc.)
- 🌐 Sub & Dub support

---

## How to install in CloudStream

1. Open **CloudStream** → **Settings** → **Extensions** → **Add Repository**
2. Paste this URL in the *Repository URL* field:

```
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME/AnimeKaiProvider/builds/repo.json
```

3. Tap **Add** / **Next**, then open the repo and tap **Download** next to *AnimeKai*.
4. Go back to the home screen, tap **None** (bottom-right), and select **AnimeKai**.

